Zetto and Kirbopher are the same entity so their slashed, and TOME is legitimately crowdfunded so it belongs in the video game category.

Please stop saying that Kids WB used an American cast for the show. The video shows proof in promos that they used Holly Garfunkle for Zeke and not Dave Kaufman. And the Toonzone forums from fans, who actually watched it, still speak of the edits.
Neddy and Pachydermus are not villains. There more of an annoyance.

Stephanie also voices KO in Jethros All Yours, We Messed Up and Level 100 so she's not replaced. I think they might switch between actors from time to time. If by episode 10 it's still Nadolny, Taylor will be replaced.
Pierre Holloway's real name is Paul Greenberg. He was properly credited in Season 2 as well as Joey D'Auria, who was credited as JW Terry
I emailed and interviewed James Fox (creator of Skatoony; Brian Boyle was not involved in the show because he left CN after the webgame) and he told me everything.
